    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained for reliable performance. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making this an excellent and dependable choice for daily driving. While there are some minor signs of normal wear and tear on the interior and exterior, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. You can expect a solid, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a great balance of value and longevity.",
